<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.278108>
    dc:description "FIGURE 1. A – E (Holotype of Protobothrops maolanensis sp. nov., SYSr 000211). A: General aspect in life; B: dorsal views of head; C: ventral views of head; D: lateral views of head; E: dorsal view of midbody (showing thin dark brown bands and keeled scales). F (Paratype, SYS r 000210): left hemipenis in asulcate view. Photographs by J. H. Yang." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/278108/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

